  <name>TKE</name>
  <summary>Coding editor based on Tcl/Tk</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      TKE is a full-featured source code editor written in Tcl/Tk.  It supports
      the following features:
    </p>
    <p>
      <ul>
        <li>Syntax highlighting</li>
        <li>Multi-cursor support</li>
        <li>Internationalization support</li>
        <li>Customizable menu bindings</li>
        <li>Clipboard history</li>
        <li>Unlimited undo/redo</li>
        <li>Language-specific snippet support</li>
        <li>Auto and smart indentation features</li>
        <li>Code line bookmarking</li>
        <li>Line number display</li>
        <li>Customizable tab stops</li>
        <li>Text transformation tools</li>
        <li>Built-in Vim support</li>
        <li>Expanded Vim functionality</li>
        <li>Regular expression in-file search/replace</li>
        <li>Regular expression multi-directory file search</li>
        <li>Symbolic searching</li>
        <li>Auto-updating on file changes external to editor</li>
        <li>File locking support</li>
        <li>Advanced command launcher</li>
        <li>File/Directory sidebar</li>
        <li>Tabbed file support</li>
        <li>Dual editor panel support</li>
        <li>Split view support</li>
        <li>Maximum column width display</li>
        <li>Automatic session saving</li>
        <li>Support for NFS-mounted file systems</li>
        <li>Plugin support</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </description>
